The method is applied to biological data, which suggests a possible connection to computer vision and image analysis. The paper also mentions the use of linear transformation, which is a common technique in neural networks and signal processing. The paper also involves the use of discriminative information, which is a common topic in neural networks and deep learning, suggesting the sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
